朴叙俊谈到《漫威》的放映时间，称他的角色“短暂”但“至关重要” https://www.nme.com/news/film/park-seo-jun-the-marvels-screen-time-short-but-crucial-3535729?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=park-seo-jun-the-漫威放映时间短但至关重要Puah ZiweiFri, 10 Nov 2023 07:59:13 +0000 Film NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3535729 <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朴叙俊的奇迹" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，这位演员只出现了大约三分钟</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/park-seo-jun-the-marvels-screen-time-short-but-crucial-3535729">朴叙俊在谈到《漫威》的上映时间时表示，他的角色“短暂”但“至关重要”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朴叙俊的奇迹" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/park-seo-jun-marvels-screen-time-getty-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>朴叙俊在新的超级英雄电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-marvels"><em>《奇迹》</em></a>中解决了他有限的放映时间。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-marvels-review-brie-larson-3532201">《漫威》评论：缺乏冲击力的古怪宇宙故事</a></strong></li></ul><p>朴叙俊在<em>《漫威》</em>中饰演燕王子。这部电影由尼亚·达科斯塔 (Nia DaCosta) 执导，是 2019 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/captain-marvel-film-review-2457783-2457783"><em>《惊奇队长》</em></a>的续集，也是电视迷你剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/ms-marvel"><em>《惊奇女士》</em></a>的延续。</p><p>这位韩国演员在影片中的亮相备受期待，但由于据报道他的上映时间有限，粉丝们对他的外表感到不满。据<em>《海峡时报》</em>报道，这位演员在新电影中的出场时间不到三分钟。</p><p>然而，据<a href="https://sbsstar.net/article/N1007418676/my-screen-time-might-be-short-but-park-seo-jun-speaks-about-his-role-in-the-marvels" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>SBS Star</em></a>报道，朴瑞俊此后解决了这些担忧，他表示“有些人可能认为我在电影中的角色太短，但我相信它在<em>漫威</em>的整体叙事中发挥着至关重要的作用”。</p><p> “我认为阿拉德娜和燕王子是展示卡罗尔·丹弗斯成长的重要地点和人物，”他补充道。 </p><p><iframe title="漫威影业的《The Marvels》 |官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wS_qbDztgVY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-marvels"><em>《漫威》</em></a>导演妮娅·达科斯塔此前透露了韩剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/itaewon-class"><em>梨泰院班</em></a>如何促使<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/park-seo-joon-the-marvels-itaewon-class-director-nia-dacosta-3529904">她在即将上映的电影中扮演朴叙俊</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，对新<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威电影宇宙</a>电影的评论也出现了分歧。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-marvels-review-brie-larson-3532201"><em>《NME》</em>给了<em>《漫威》</em>三颗星的评价</a>，称“虽然<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/candyman-interview-nia-dacosta-yahya-abdul-mateen-3028640">达科斯塔的<i>《糖果人》</i>重启令人兴奋</a>，但它从来没有达到同样水平的参与度”。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2023/11/08/the-marvels-review-brie-larson/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《每日电讯报》</i></a>写道，这部电影在一星评论中将超级英雄系列“推向了新低”，而<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/the-marvels/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《帝国》杂志</i></a>则给了这部电影四颗星，称其为“该工作室在某些领域制作的最轻松、最平静的电影”。时间”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/some-critics-think-the-marvels-has-taken-the-mcu-to-a-new-low-3534864">看看其他评论家对这部新电影的看法</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-marvels-soundtrack-heres-every-song-in-the-movie-3534282">“漫威”原声带：这是电影中的每首歌</a></strong></li></ul><p>其他消息方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/song-kang-sweet-home-season-two-teaser-netflix-3535777">Netflix 发布了热门韩剧<em>《甜蜜之家》</em>第二季的新预告片</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/park-seo-jun-the-marvels-screen-time-short-but-crucial-3535729">朴叙俊在谈到《漫威》的上映时间时表示，他的角色“短暂”但“至关重要”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
